Former BBNaija housemate, Ka3na has responded to the mockery of her accent on the reunion show. Ka3na, who seems to be the highlight of the BBNaija reunion show, has been mocked for her accent by Nigerians since the beginning of the show. The mother of one who refers to herself as ‘Boss lady’ urged Nigerians to stop judging her and just enjoy the show. BBNaija reunion: Ka3na admits having sex with Praise, says he didn’t last 5 seconds According to her, her flourishing lifestyle and businesses was obtained by Brain work not speaking ‘English’. Her tweet read: “If anyone of you is without sin, be the first to throw a stone at her. Otherwise! Chill in your sitting room and enjoy the show. “No be English I use buy my houses and my numerous businesses oh! Na brain work.”